	Leo a killer    
	 Los Angeles, Nov. 2 (PTI): Actor Leonardo DiCaprio is turning villain in the film adaptation of The Devil in the White City where he will play a charming serial killer prowling the streets of 1993 Chicago.       
	Erik Larsons acclaimed novel was on the New York Times bestseller list for three years. It has sold 2.3 million copies and has been translated into 17 languages.       
	The story, which has fascinated Hollywood, is based on the lives of two men who turned the 1893 Chicago World Fair into their playground.
                                                                                                                                                      
